        "Description": "Good evening 47, your next job is settled in Sapienza, Italy. The client wants us to eliminate the mayroal candidate and his lawyer who both are affiliated with the Mafia. We also detected the presence of two more agents that will keep an eye on the place to ensure the meeting of the two principal targets.\r\rYou know what to do.\r\rGood mission 47.",
